$group
    $
        var sect = {
            title: 'Concepts'
        };

    section(&sect)

        p The Wizzi Factory is a general purpose and language agnostic artifact generator.
        
        p It is model driven and regard software as a data structure that is generated processing data structures.
            \b Its inputs and outputs are printable and human readable streams of characters.
            
        p It is an open tool for the development environment, with no runtime.